<section id="Section520261">
   <title>
       
      <indexterm significance="normal">
         <primary>items</primary>
         <secondary>by class code</secondary>
      </indexterm> 
      <indexterm significance="normal">
         <primary>class codes</primary>
         <secondary>item details for</secondary>
      </indexterm>Items by Class Code</title>
   <para>To view Items by Class Code, select the "Items by
    Class Code" option. The following screen will appear:</para>
   <para>
      <screenshot>
         <mediaobject>
            <imageobject>
               <imagedata fileref="images/PD_Disp_itemsClassCode.png" id="Graphic563623"/>
            </imageobject>
            <caption id="Caption520267">Items by Class Code</caption>
         </mediaobject>
      </screenshot>
   </para>
   <para>When displaying Items by Class Code, you are
    presented with the following options:</para>
   <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
         <term>All Class Codes</term>
         <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1923d38">
            <para>Select to display Items for all Class Codes.</para>
         </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
         <term>Selected</term>
         <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1923d80">
            <para>Specify Class Code whose Items you want to display.</para>
         </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
         <term>Pattern</term>
         <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1923dc8">
            <para>Enter a Class Code pattern to select a range of Class
          Codes.</para>
            <para>Refine your search using Regular Expressions,
          as described in <xref endterm="Anchor77806" linkend="Anchor77806"/>.</para>
         </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
         <term>Show Inactive Items</term>
         <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x192ba00">
            <para>Select to show Inactive Items in the display.</para>
         </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
         <term>Items</term>
         <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x192ba48">
            <para>Display lists Items by Class Code, using the specified
          parameters.</para>
         </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
   <para>To the far right of the screen, the following
    buttons are available:</para>
   <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
         <term>CLOSE</term>
         <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x192bab4">
            <para>Closes the screen, returning you to the application
          desktop.</para>
         </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
         <term>QUERY</term>
         <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x192bafc">
            <para>Select to generate the display, using the specified
          parameters.</para>
         </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
         <term>PRINT</term>
         <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x192bb44">
            <para>Runs the report associated with this screen.</para>
         </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
   <para>Right-clicking on an Item in the Items list enables
    you to select from the following options:</para>
   <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
         <term>Edit Item Master</term>
         <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x192bbb0">
            <para/>
         </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../widgets/xtreewidget.xml" xpointer="element(xtreewidget.menu.exportcontents)"/>
    </variablelist>
  </section>
